  "remarks": "Tactical Missiles Corporation develops, manufactures, modernises, repairs and maintains strategic and tactical aviation high-precision air-to-surface and air-to-air weapon systems and unified maritime weapon systems of the Russian armed forces. Weapons manufactured by Tactical Missiles Corporation were used by Russia during the unprovoked military aggression against Ukraine in 2022.",
